text: Sarah Trösch (born 28 September 1994) is a Swiss volleyball player. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She participated at the 2017 Montreux Volley Masters. She plays for NUC VOLLEYBALL. == Clubs == * Viteos Neuchatel Université (2017) * Volley Lugano (2018–) == References == == External links == * CEV profile * SARAH TRÖSCH NUOVO PALLEGGIO LNA Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
